      "sender": "DevOps",
      "message": "Plain request IDs aren't enough for tracing. `get_log()` should now return a list of dicts: `{\"id\": <request_id>, \"seq\": <1-based sequence number>}`. Sequence resets per service.",
      "additional_test_cases": [
